ZH: 保佑我的家庭幸福快乐。
EN: Bless my family with happiness and joy.
ZH: 请保佑我的朋友们能够平安健康。
EN: Please bless my friends with safety and good health.
ZH: 我被这次考试保佑了，拿到了满分。
EN: I was blessed by this exam and got a perfect score.
ZH: 保佑我在工作中能够取得巨大的成功。
EN: Bless me with great success in my job.
ZH: 我请求你保佑我找到一个好工作。
EN: I ask for your blessing to find a good job.
ZH: 愿上帝保佑所有需要帮助的人。
EN: May God bless all those in need of help.
ZH: 保佑我的家人在新的一年里平平安安。
EN: Bless my family with peace and safety in the new year.
ZH: 请保佑我的父母健康长寿。
EN: Please bless my parents with good health and long life.
ZH: 保佑我在考试中取得优异的成绩。
EN: Bless me with excellent grades in the exams.
ZH: 我祈求上天保佑这个世界充满和平。
EN: I pray for God's blessing to fill this world with peace.
ZH: 保佑我的梦想能够实现。
EN: Bless my dreams to come true.
ZH: 请保佑我的孩子们能够快乐成长。
EN: Please bless my children to grow up happily.
ZH: 愿神保佑我找到真爱。
EN: May God bless me to find true love.
ZH: 保佑我在这次旅行中平安归来。
EN: Bless me to return safely from this trip.
ZH: 请保佑我的宠物能够健康快乐。
EN: Please bless my pet to be healthy and happy.
ZH: 我每天都为你的幸福保佑。
EN: I bless you for your happiness every day.
ZH: 愿上帝保佑我顺利度过难关。
EN: May God bless me to overcome difficulties successfully.
ZH: 保佑我和我的爱人永远在一起。
EN: Bless me and my loved one to be together forever.
ZH: 请保佑我在现在的工作上取得突破。
EN: Please bless me to make a breakthrough in my current job.
ZH: 我祈求上帝保佑我们的国家繁荣昌盛。
EN: I pray for God's blessing for our country to prosper.
